Package kin.sdk.exception

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AccountDeletedException
    Account was deleted using KinClient.deleteAccount(int), and cannot be used any more.
    AccountNotFoundException
    Account was not created on the blockchain
    CorruptedDataException
    Input exported account data is corrupted and cannot be imported.
    CreateAccountException  
    CryptoException
    Decryption/Encryption error when importing - KinClient.importAccount(String, String) or exporting KinAccount.export(String) an account.
    DeleteAccountException  
    IllegalAmountException
    amount was not legal
    InsufficientFeeException  
    InsufficientKinException
    Transaction failed due to insufficient kin.
    LoadAccountException  
    OperationFailedException  
    TransactionFailedException
    Blockchain transaction failure has happened, contains blockchain specific error details
